name: FREQAI
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
The Razor’s Edge finally puts the tools in the hands of the consumer. Our mission statement is simple: Algorithmic Intellingence is the key for surviving a complex ever evolving market and should be made widely available. We do not make false promises of MASSIVE 1000x gains, or unrealistic Ponzi scheme APYs. What we will deliver is consistent, automatic, 24/7 running strategies. Our bots will constantly scrape for 2-5% gains. Our treasury will constantly compound these gains. Thus, FREQAI will continually deliver small wins while our holders merely gain passive ETH Rewards.
All Treasury Taxes will be used to trade by the FREQ AI trade bots as explained earlier in the white paper.
